  "promotion_rules": {
    "A+": "Allowed when every displayed race row has public-safe race-by-race post time plus minimal race metadata: race title, distance, and surface/course type. Do not store starter lists, odds, results, payouts, predictions, full racecard text, or raw HTML.",
